title: Canada 's biodiesel production 2007 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Production in million liters. In total the number of data points it has is 13.
In general Production in million liters has rose over the Year.
The line drastically increased by 2.2 times from Year 2013 to 2014.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2013 and 2014.
Maximum Production in million liters, about 463.0 was reported at Year 2016
Minimum Production in million liters about 70.0 was reached at Year 2007
min_summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Production in million liters. In total the number of data points it has is 13.
Overall Production in million liters has increased over the Year.

Production in million liters is roughly constant from 2007 to 2012, rapidly increasing from 2012 to 2014, roughly constant from 2014 to 2015, slightly increasing from 2015 to 2016, roughly constant from 2016 to 2017, and lastly roughly increasing from 2017 to 2019.
